<item>
            <title>[DOXIA-433] Regression: Unicode characters not rendered in table cells</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/DOXIA-433</link>
                <project id="12317230" key="DOXIA">Maven Doxia (Moved to GitHub Issues)</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;After upgrading the maven-site-plugin from version 2.0.1 to 2.3, I noticed that one of my APT files in which unicode characters are used is no longer rendered correctly to HTML. More precisely, in the APT file there are several occurrences of&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;   \u2713&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The generated HTML file then contains&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;   &amp;#xa0;u2713&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;rather than&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;   &amp;#x2713;&lt;/p&gt;


&lt;p&gt;I do not have a minimal example attached, but it should be easily reproducible using Maven 2.2.1 and site plugin 2.3 (you might also want to try with 2.0.1 where it works for me).&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment>Maven 2.2.1, site plugin 2.3</environment>
