                            <comment id="14431963" author="ltheussl" created="Wed, 1 Jun 2011 13:26:46 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I cannot reproduce this, it works here. See attached test project. Can you confirm?&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14431863" author="twwwt" created="Wed, 1 Jun 2011 14:18:20 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Yes, I can confirm that your example works also for me. However, after checking again, I&apos;ve found that the issue seems to occur only when used inside table cells. Attached you will find an example. Simply copy this file into src/site/apt and run mvn site again. Also, change the version in the POM back to 2.0.1 and then it should work.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
